OL,3,CWes Streeting resigns, paving way for
OL,4,Cleadership coup against Starmer
OL,6,FWes Streeting resigned on Thursday but
OL,7,Fstopped short of triggering a
OL,8,Fleadership election. ITV News
OL,9,FPolitical Correspondent Shehab Khan
OL,10,Freports.
OL,12,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting has
OL,13,Fresigned, paving the way for a
OL,14,Fpotential leadership bid against Prime
OL,15,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
