PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778825170
OL,3,CWes Streeting resigns, paving way for
OL,4,Cleadership coup against Starmer
OL,6,FIn a letter to the prime minister,
OL,7,FStreeting wrote: "Having lost
OL,8,Fconfidence in your leadership, I have
OL,9,Fconcluded that it would be
OL,10,Fdishonourable and unprincipled to do
OL,11,Fso (stay in post)."
OL,13,FHe continued: "Where we need vision,
OL,14,Fwe have a vacuum. Where we need
OL,15,Fdirection, we have drift. This was
OL,16,Funderscored by your speech on Monday.
OL,26,@sD@DpmsD@Qpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778825170
OL,3,CWes Streeting resigns, paving way for
OL,4,Cleadership coup against Starmer
OL,6,F"Leaders take responsibility, but too
OL,7,Foften that has meant other people
OL,8,Ffalling on their swords. You also need
OL,9,Fto listen to your colleagues,
OL,10,Fincluding backbenchers, and the heavy-
OL,11,Fhanded approach to dissenting voices
OL,12,Fdiminishes our politics."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
