OL,3,CWes Streeting resigns, paving way for
OL,4,Cleadership coup against Starmer
OL,6,FIt comes after he met with Starmer on
OL,7,FWednesday, in crunch talks that only
OL,8,Flasted 16 minutes and seemed to have
OL,9,Fleft the pair at a political impasse.
OL,11,FThe health secretary has become the
OL,12,Ffirst of Starmer's cabinet to launch a
OL,13,Fcoup against him.
OL,15,FThe PM has been facing headwinds
OL,16,Fwithin his own party since last week's
OL,17,Fdevastating results in the local,
OL,18,FScottish and Welsh elections.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
