PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778825170
OL,3,CWes Streeting resigns, paving way for
OL,4,Cleadership coup against Starmer
OL,6,FAllies of the former health secretary
OL,7,Finsist Streeting has these numbers,
OL,8,Fbut until a contest is officially
OL,9,Flaunched it is unclear exactly how
OL,10,Fmuch support Streeting carries.
OL,12,FGreen Party leader Zack Polanski
OL,13,Fresponded to Streeting's resignation,
OL,14,Fsaying his leadership would be "more
OL,15,Fof the same, but even worse, a
OL,16,Ffactional and divisive politician."
OL,18,FPolanski pointed to the former health
OL,19,Fsecretary's past association with Lord
OL,20,FPeter Mandelson.
OL,26,@vD@`OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
