OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778825170
OL,3,CWes Streeting resigns, paving way for
OL,4,Cleadership coup against Starmer
OL,6,F"If Labour thinks Wes Streeting is the
OL,7,Fanswer, they obviously don't know the
OL,8,Fquestion the country is asking," he
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FLabour backbencher Jonathan Brash
OL,12,Freiterated his call for Sir Keir
OL,13,FStarmer to set out a timetable for his
OL,14,Fdeparture following Wes Streeting's
OL,15,Fresignation from Cabinet.
OL,17,FThe Hartlepool MP posted on X: "The
OL,18,Fcall for a broad contest with the best
OL,19,Fpossible field of candidates is
OL,20,Fabsolutely right from Wes Streeting.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@`O]yD@`OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
