OL,3,CWes Streeting resigns, paving way for
OL,4,Cleadership coup against Starmer
OL,6,FThe former Deputy PM, Angela Rayner,
OL,7,Fhas signalled she may be prepared to
OL,8,Fstand in a leadership election,
OL,9,Frefusing to rule it out in an
OL,10,Finterview with ITV News.
OL,12,FRayner resigned as Deputy PM after
OL,13,Fbecoming embroiled in a dispute over
OL,14,Fthe tax she paid on a property in
OL,15,FBrighton.
OL,17,FThat came to an end on Thursday, with
OL,18,FRayner claiming she had been cleared
OL,19,Fby HMRC, paying the correct amount of
OL,20,Ftax.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
