OL,3,CWes Streeting resigns, paving way for
OL,4,Cleadership coup against Starmer
OL,6,FThe other contender facing their own
OL,7,Fhurdles is the current mayor of
OL,8,FManchester, Andy Burnham.
OL,10,FBurnham backers favour a longer
OL,11,Fleadership contest, which would give
OL,12,Fhim the time to become an MP and throw
OL,13,Fhis own name into the ring.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
